The DTMF frequencies are divided as follows: Low-frequency row tones (697 Hz, 770 Hz, 852 Hz, and 941 Hz) and high-frequency column tones (1209 Hz, 1336 Hz, 1477 Hz, and 1633 Hz). The given frequency pair is 941 Hz from the low-frequency group and 1477 Hz from the high-frequency group. By referencing the standard DTMF frequency table, this frequency pair (941 Hz and 1477 Hz) corresponds to the '#' key on a DTMF keypad.
